problem_prompt:
Approach the following question the way someone with a PhD in mathematics would. What is the SMILES expression of (3R)-1-(2H-tetrazol-5-yl)pyrrolidin-3-ol?
Answer:
gpt_response:
The SMILES expression of (3R)-1-(2H-tetrazol-5-yl)pyrrolidin-3-ol can be written as:

CC1CNC[C@@H](O1)c1nnc(n1)N

This SMILES expression encodes the structural information of the molecule in a compact and standardized format, allowing for easy representation and manipulation in computer systems.
